text: Sadia Khateeb is an Indian actress and Model. She made her acting debut with Shikara (2020), directed by Vidhu Vinod Chopra Khateeb was studying electrical engineering before her debut film. She was born and raised in Jammu and Kahsmir, India. Her acting has been praised by critics. ==Filmography== Shikara Directed by Vidhu Vinod Chopra ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian film actresses Category:21st-century Indian actresses
